    "notes": "Phase-0 simple local-linear fit (no SBI yet). Design is effectively sharp: of 302 schools below -0.5, only 1 are excluded by the floor's CI condition (P8CIUPP\u003e=0). DIFFERENTIAL ATTRITION CAVEAT: within +/-0.5 of the cutoff, 21.5% of below-floor schools vs 11.3% of above-floor schools lack a linked 2017/18 P8 (sponsored academies are re-issued a new URN). This attrition is correlated with treatment and biases the complete-case estimate; it is the dominant threat to this mark and motivates the Phase-1 attrition-aware treatment."
